tlement_price_variable="{low} - {high}",pr_loan_div_placeholder_max_amt="Max {amount}",pr_loan_top_title_target_amount="Target amount",pr_loan_top_text_pledge_amount="Pledge amount",pr_loan_top_title_principle_repaid="Total repayment",pr_loan_mid_title_instlm_plan="Installment plan",pr_loan_mid_text_period_months="{period} months",pr_loan_bot_btn_continue="Continue",pr_loan_top_text_max_amount="The maximum target amount is {maxamount}",pr_loan_top_text_min_amount="The minimum target amount is {minamount}",pr_loan_faq_title_loan_instlm="Loan instalment",pr_loan_faq_desc_hold_for_long="Hold BTC and ETH at a lower price for a long-term bullish outlook",pr_loan_faq_desc_flexible_repayment="Flexible repayment periods to ease your financial pressure",pr_loan_faq_desc_seize_opportunity="Seize the opportunity despite market trends",pr_loan_faq_title_what_kind_users="What kind of users is Loan Installment suitable for?",pr_loan_faq_desc_product_suits="This product is suitable for users who have already held crypto that have been bullish for a long time and hope to purchase more BTC and ETH through installment payments.",pr_loan_faq_title_what_is_loan="What is Loan installment and what are the product rules?",pr_loan_faq_desc_loan_instlm_is="Loan Installment is a product that helps users buy a specific currency in installments at the current currency price.\n \nSuppose you hold 1 BTC and it has been bullish for a long time. The current currency price is 15,000 USDT/BTC. Your goal is to purchase an additional 1 BTC at a price of 15,000 USDT/BTC during the year. At this time, you can use Loan Installment to set the target hoarding amount to 2 BTC (you already hold 1 BTC and need to purchase an additional one), deposit the 1 BTC you hold, and choose a 12-month repayment plan. After paying off the final outstanding amount, you will possess 2 BTC in the fund account.\"",pr_loan_faq_title_what_currencies="What currencies are currently supported? ",pr_loan_faq_desc_support_btc_eth="We currently support BTC and ETH only.",pr_loan_faq_title_how_many="How many installment repayment options are available?",pr_loan_faq_desc_support_month="We currently support 3, 6 and 12 month repayments.",pr_loan_faq_title_why_deposit="After entering the target amount, why do I need to deposit a certain amount of assets as collateral ?",pr_loan_faq_desc_specific_formula="To ensure that you can purchase relevant assets in installments at the current price, you need to deposit a certain amount of assets when using this product. \nThe specific formula is as follows:\nTarget amount = amount that you need to deposit + additional amount purchased during the period\nYou need to deposit an amount equal to 0.5 * target amount.\nFor example, if you hold 1 BTC and set the target hoarding amount to 1.6 BTC, you need to deposit 0.8 BTC (1.6 * 0.5)",pr_loan_faq_title_what_risks="What risks does the product have?",pr_loan_faq_desc_if_price_drop="If the currency price drops to a certain value, the installment order for hoarding currency applied by the user will be automatically cancelled. However, the previously deposited assets will not be recovered and you won't need to continue to repay the installments.",pr_loan_card_text_pledge_assets="In order to use this product, you need to pledge assets of 0.5*target amount as collateral. Your pledged collateral and the {crypto} you purchased with installment will be fully released to your Funding account after you complete your final repayment.",pr_loan_card_text1_equal_repayment="The repayment rule is equal principal, the interest rate changes at an hourly rate, and the interest will be included in the total repayment amount and repaid in the last instalment.",pr_loan_home_title_loan_instlm="Loan installment",pr_loan_home_text_hold_instlm="Hold BTC/ETH at a lower price with flexible installment plans",pr_loan_div_tag_hot="HOT",pr_loan_list_item1_target_amount="Target amount",pr_loan_list_item2_total_repayment="Total liability",pr_loan_