ate goes above {apy1} you'll be eligible for up to {apy2} APY.",pr_earn_simpleearn_subscription_list_subtitle_now="Now",pr_earn_simpleearn_subscription_text_agreement="Simple Earn user agreement",pr_earn_simpleearn_subscription_text_kyc_verification="Pass the {kyc2} verification and are eligible to get a min. of {apy} APY on the first {tokenNum} {tokenName} you subscribe.",pr_earn_simpleearn_subscription_toast_sold_out="The product had sold out",pr_sharkfin_card_text_opens_on="Opens on",pr_dualinvest_subscribe_modal_rate_pophover="It may change based on the market condition. Please check the final rate on the order confirmation page.",pr_holding_header_title_product_name="Dual Investment Lite",pr_holding_body_title_term="Term",pr_dualinvest_body_termtips_day="{days} day",pr_dualinvest_body_termtips_days="{days} days",pr_holding_body_card_apy="Est. APY",pr_holding_body_orderinfo_auto_sell="Target price",pr_holding_input_title_subscription_amount="Subscription amount",pr_holding_deposit_btn_all="All",pr_holding_input_btn_all="All",pr_holding_guide_modaltext_returns="Returns",pr_holding_bot_btn_confirm="Confirm",pr_holding_mid_link_more_products="More products",pr_dualinvest_dialog_info_btc_index_price="Current {currency} price {price}",pr_holding_card_text_if_price_above="If {crypto} price is < {amount}, you'll receive",pr_holding_card_text_if_price_below="If {crypto} price is > {amount}, you'll receive",pr_dualinvest_order_start_time="Start time",pr_dualinvest_order_end_time="End time",pr_holding_deposit_input_min="Min {min}",pr_holding_subscribe_modal_confirm="Confirm",pr_holding_mid_text_product="Product",pr_holding_mid_text_subscription_amount="Subscription amount",pr_holding_body_title_return_payment="You'll receive",pr_holding_subscribe_modal_confirm_agreement="I have read and agree to {agreement}",pr_holding_footer_checkbox_useragreement="Dual Investment Lite User Agreement",pr_holding_footer_checkbox_useragreement_url="/support/hc/en-us/articles/7079035382541",pr_holding_body_card_returnpayment_details_new="If the {crypto} price is higher than or equal to {price} on the expiration date, your {notipcrypto} will be automatically sold at {price}, and you'll receive {amount}.",pr_holding_body_cardtips_index="Avg. price on the expiration date at 07:00 - 08:00 UTC",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_yield="Is the APY fixed?",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_yield_details="Yes, the APY is fixed. Once the order is confirmed, the APY won't change. You can find the APY of your subscribed product on the order page.",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_currency="Can I choose which crypto I'll receive for my returns?",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_currency_details="No, the crypto you receive depends on whether the crypto you've invested in reaches the target price on the expiration date. For example, if you invest in BTC, you'll receive USDT if the BTC price reaches the target price on the expiration date. If BTC doesn't reach the target price, you'll receive your returns in BTC.",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_returnpayment="When will I receive my returns?",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_returnpayment_details="Your returns will be settled at 10:00 UTC on the expiration date. However, it may take up to 24 hours for your returns to show up in your Fuding account.",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_redemption="What are the redemption rules? *aligned with Dual Investment",pr_holding_bot_intro_faq_redemption_details="Can I redeem before the expiration date?\nYes, you can apply for early redemption if the term is longer than 2 days and your subscription has been active for more than 24 hours. The deadline for early redemption is 24 hours before the expiration date and time.\nFor example, if the subscription start time is Mar 1, 08:00 UTC and the expiration time is June 24, 08:00 UTC, you can apply for early redemption from Mar 2, 08:00 UTC - June 23, 08:00 UTC.\nWhen will I receive my returns if I redeem early?\nYou'll usually receive your returns in your Funding account around 10:00 UTC the day after redemption.\nWill I lose money if I redeem early?\nIt's possible to lose money if you redeem early. Use caution before initiating early redemption and check whether the redemption is lower than your subscription amount. You can check the final amount that you'll receive after redemption on the confirmation page.",pr_dualinvest_bot_title_subscribe_rules="How it works",pr_holding_guide_modaltitle_settlement_rules="Settlement rules",pr_dualinvest_redemption_modal_rules_start="Start time: {time}",pr_dualinvest_redemption_modal_rules_end="End time: {time}",pr_holding_guide_modaltext_settlement_rules="If the expiration price is lower than the target price, you'll receive your returns in {currency}.\n\nReturns = Subscription amount x (1 + term rate) {currency}.\n\nIf the expiration price is higher than, or equal to, the target price, you'll receive returns in {stablecoins}.\n\nReturns = Subscription amount x Target price x (1 + Term rate) {stablecoins}.\n\nThe expiration price refers to the average index price of {currency}. It's set between 07:00 UTC and 08:00 UTC on the expiration date.",pr_holding_guide_modaltext_target_price_desc="The crypto you'll receive is determined on whether its market price reaches the target price",pr_holding_mid_text_term_variable="{time} ({days})",pr_holding_footer_btn_confirm="Confirm",pr_holding_deposit_btn_continue="Confirm",pr_holding_deposit_tips_minamount="Min subscription amount {amount}",pr_holding_deposit_tips_maxamount="Max subscription amount {amount}",pr_holding_body_title_amount="Amount",pr_finance_common_amount_currency="{num} {currency}",pr_holding_footer_tips_final_apy="The estimated APY on this page is subject to market fluctuations. You can find the confirmed APY once you've confirmed your order.",pr_holding_body_tips_return_time="Settlement time: {time}",pr_holding_body_tips_expire_time="Expiration time {time}",pr_holding_body_tips_start_time="Interest accrual time {time}",pr_holding_body_title_confirmation_inform